{"word":"διατηρέω","slug":"διατηρέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>διατηρέω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:διά\">διά</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:τηρέω\">τηρέω</a></el> ‘watch, guard’] <b><i>guard carefully</i></b> <el>δ. πάντα τὰ ῥήματα ταύτα <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐν\">ἐν</a> τῇ ϰαρδίᾳ αὐτῆς</el> <i>in her heart she was treating all these things as a treasure</i> <b><a href='B:490 2:51'>Lk 2:51</a>;</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐξ\">ἐξ</a> ὧν διατηροῦντες ἐαυτούς</el> <i>from which preserving yourselves</i> <b><a href='B:510 15:29'>Ac 15:29</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:διατέταγμαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:διατί\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}